Open Links in New Tabs#using md#For Kramdown, e.g. Jekyll:
[clickable-text](link-url){:target=&#34;_blank&#34;} In general, the format in Kramdown is {: attribute1=&quot;value1&quot; attribute2=&quot;value2&quot;}
For pandoc:
[clickable-text](link-url){target=&#34;_blank&#34;} In general, the format in Kramdown is {attribute1=&quot;value1&quot; attribute2=&quot;value2&quot;} (w/o :)
However, this will NOT work if using hidden separated reference (except Grav CMS).
